OL,5, A boy who picked up a firework which   
OL,6, exploded in his hand is struggling with
OL,7, severe nightmares, his dad has said.   
OL,9,FKyran, nine, was playing with his      
OL,10,Ffriend Bradley, when a firework was    
OL,11,Fallegedly thrown into their den on a   
OL,12,Ffield in Hengoed, Caerphilly county.   
OL,14,FHis dad Liam said: "One of his most    
OL,15,Fvivid memories is watching his fingers 
OL,16,Ffall off as he was walking home."      
OL,18,FGwent Police are investigating and have
OL,19,Fappealed for witnesses.                
